As twilight settles  
a tranquil shadow,  
I listen to the wind  
      singing softly,  
    nature’s lullaby bringing  
  a beautiful peace to  
    the heart.  
  
 - Jack Kerouac  

*(from "The Sea is My Brother")*

- Jack Kerouac
